Create executable file for Windows. You need Python 3.13.13 (or later), Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable 2017 (or later) and PyInstaller. (pip install pyinstaller)
Command for Windows: pyinstaller --windowed --onefile "\Path\your\file\Neo Browser.py"
Create executable file for Linux (Debian/Ubuntu Distributions) You need python3 and these libraries:
python3-pyqt5
python3-pyqt5.qtwebengine
python3-requests
python3-pyaudio
pyinstaller.
Linux command: pyinstaller --onefile "/Path/Your/Location/Neo Browser.py"
Thanks for using Neo Browser!

